But we need $\mathbb{E}[X_{\tau \wedge \sigma}] \leq \mathbb{E}[X_\tau \mid \mathcal{F}_\sigma]$.

So we need to relate $\mathbb{E}[X_\sigma \mid \mathcal{F}_{\tau \wedge \sigma}]$ to $\mathbb{E}[X_\tau \mid \mathcal{F}_\sigma]$.

